This reverts commit e66945ac2b579b57d3d0698ee97a36fa9b563369 because one of the committers was not properly given credit (possibly due to the merged commit messages). 

The PR was based on his commits.

@tysonnorris Sorry about that. I had left a [note](https://github.com/apache/incubator-openwhisk/pull/3669#issuecomment-389893508) to tweak the commit message. I will prepare a follow on PR with the proper commit message that will credit the original PR author as well.
